{
  "stem": "26576.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was later on a standing joke, because everybody was very impressed the way that I came to the police station, and they asked me, what is your name?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said Masha.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said, the second name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, I haven't got a second name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And finally, because I-- I couldn't work out but-- later on, my father was scared probably that I will sort charge him with something.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I go to head out of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so everywhere, whenever they needed things to be done, if it was-- I mean if it included Polish, I would go and do the job.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were-- yes, although they were not religious, because-- At that stage, belonging to Bund was, in a way-- the Bund was-- I don't want to go into political discussions.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the Bund tried very hard to make people-- they were socialists, and they were not believers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But-- but they still were quite traditional, let's say.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we would have a Seder.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like I remember before Yom Tov, we'd always go and buy wine and buy macaroons.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we will-- the children will get new clothes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then so later on in life, religious or not, we tried to keep-- to keep it always.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we had Passover.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was also very often invited like for-- like some of the neighbors would have Sukkot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would invite the children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my grandmother will go to that Sukkot and would look out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't celebrate every Yom Tov.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we did celebrate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So in a way, today you would call it traditional Jews without religion, without going to synagogue, because my father did not go to synagogue.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The main languages that we spoke was Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I spoke Polish in school and with my friends.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
